Simple Web Manager.
Version: 1.0.
Author: Marin Alcaraz.


Simple Web Manager is an easy and basic tool to manage Archlinux (rackspace cloud) Webservers.

SWM can perform:

1.-Add Website.
2.-Delete Website.
3.-Create Database.
4.-Create Database_user.
5.-Manage database_user permissions.

Instructions:

1.-Upload the SWM file to your server. (You should check the file path inside the file and verify it matches with your server)
2.-Grant executions permissions to the file.
3.-Run the file.
4.-Enjoy.
